result.title: CodeForces Round #118 (Div. 1/2)
result.content:
I have just added codeforces round 118 to this group!

It seems that we cannot set time unfortunately.

But it also means that we don't need to be concerned with time difference since we are virtually participating!

You can discuss problems here once you finished the contest.

It means that you should not look at comments before participation!

Let me know if you enjoyed it and if you liked it!

I will greatly appreciate any sort of comment regarding how we should host contests and such!

GL&HF!
